  <brief_title>A Dose Ranging Study to Compare the Safety and Efficacy of Aliskiren in Patients With High Blood Pressure</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group, Multicenter Study Comparing an Eight-week Treatment of Aliskiren 75 mg, 150 mg and 300 mg to Placebo in Patients With Essential Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
